reviewText: I watched the series of Wild At Heart on Net flex and loved it I plan on buying it .They didn't show the ending there that was so upsetting I would love to know how it ended .Did Danny's wife come back with there child ?
I love this series and such a great family series without cursing or nudity. I have watched 60 shows out of the series so far. The worst thing is that I am about to come to the end of them.
